<refsynopsisdiv id="bg_console.synopsis">
  <title>Synopsis</title>
  <cmdsynopsis><command>bg_console [-hewvr] [ OPTIONS ] </command>
  </cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1 id="bg_console.options">
    <title>Arguments</title>
    <para>Accepted arguments:</para>
    <variablelist>
        <varlistentry>
            <term><option>--properties</option></term>
            <listitem>
            <para>The bg.properties configuration file to use.</para>
            </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
            <term><option>-h --help</option></term>
            <listitem>
            <para>usage </para>
            </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
            <term><option>-v --verbose level</option></term>
            <listitem>
            <para>Set logging levels for the console loggers. </para>
            </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
            <term><option>--host portpair </option></term>
            <listitem>
            <para> port pair for connecting to mmcs_server, 
              defaults to 127.0.0.1:32031
	    </para>
            </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
            <term><option>-w --waitforserver </option></term>
            <listitem>
            <para> 
	      Wait for mmcs_server if it's not already started.
	    </para>
            </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
            <term><option>-r --auto-reconnect true|false </option></term>
            <listitem>
            <para> 
	      Automatically reconnect to mmcs_server if it is restarted.  Defaults to true.
	    </para>
            </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
            <term><option>-v --version </option></term>
            <listitem>
            <para> 
	      Display version information.
	    </para>
            </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
            <term><option>-e --eof-exit </option></term>
            <listitem>
            <para> 
	      Terminate after reading a script.
	    </para>
            </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

    </variablelist>

</refsect1>

<refsect1 id="bg_console.description">
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>bg_console is the BlueGene/Q administrative console.  It interfaces with the 
BlueGene/Q control system components to perform a systems management tasks
through a large number of internal and external commands.  Consult the bg_console
help system for further details.</para>
</refsect1>


